  "instructions": [
    "Place the beef shin in a large pot, cover with water and add low-sodium beef broth.",
    "Add bay leaves and thyme sprigs. Bring to a boil then reduce heat to a simmer.",
    "Cook at a gentle simmer for 6-8 hours until tender. Check internal temperature should reach at least 71°C (160°F).",
